LIST OF COMPONENTS

ICs
1. CD4060 – Oscillator and frequency divider (2 pcs)
2. CD4026 – Decade counter & 7-segment display driver (6 pcs)
3. 7408 – Quad 2-input AND gate (1 pc)
4. 7805 Voltage Regulator – For regulated 5V output (1 pcs) {Note: usually we are getting 9v battery }

Displays
1. 7-Segment Display (Common Cathode) – For time digits (6 pcs)

Crystal and Passive Components
1. Crystal Oscillator – 32.768 kHz (1 pc)
2. Resistors – 470ohm(43),10K(2)
3. Capacitors – 33 pico farad (1)
4. Diodes – 1N4007
5. Connecting wires
6. Bread board ( as per the requirement )

Controls
1. Push Buttons – For Reset and Set functions (number as required)

Power Supply
1. 9V Battery – Power source (1 pc)
